{
    "publish_date": "2015-04-15T22:51:08.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT5M", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "- So, a couple of days ago", 
            "dur": "0.813", 
            "start": "0.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was catching up with\na friend over drinks.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "1.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were sitting down chatting,", 
            "dur": "1.341", 
            "start": "2.929"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I turn to order\nanother beer, when he said,", 
            "dur": "1.686", 
            "start": "4.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Are you sure dude?", 
            "dur": "0.975", 
            "start": "5.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Don&#39;t you glow?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.097", 
            "start": "6.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was like, &quot;Glow?", 
            "dur": "1.158", 
            "start": "8.028"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What the hell you talking about?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.301", 
            "start": "9.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And he said, &quot;You know,", 
            "dur": "0.934", 
            "start": "10.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;well, when Asian people drink", 
            "dur": "1.199", 
            "start": "11.421"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;their faces get red.", 
            "dur": "0.996", 
            "start": "12.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;You know, Asian glow.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.178", 
            "start": "13.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I didn&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "1.158", 
            "start": "14.794"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What was this Asian\nglow he&#39;s talking about?", 
            "dur": "1.788", 
            "start": "15.952"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And why did he think I had it?", 
            "dur": "1.483", 
            "start": "17.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And finally, is it actually a real thing?", 
            "dur": "2.011", 
            "start": "19.223"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(&quot;Ergo&quot;)", 
            "dur": "4.852", 
            "start": "21.234"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, to start my quest,", 
            "dur": "1.438", 
            "start": "26.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I took the question to the streets of LA.", 
            "dur": "2.377", 
            "start": "27.524"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, do you guys know what Asian glow is?", 
            "dur": "1.686", 
            "start": "29.901"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Have no clue.", 
            "dur": "1.585", 
            "start": "31.587"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- No.", 
            "dur": "0.894", 
            "start": "33.172"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I never seen it.", 
            "dur": "0.934", 
            "start": "34.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- A lot of my peers were Asian,", 
            "dur": "2.743", 
            "start": "35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they refused to drink", 
            "dur": "2.072", 
            "start": "37.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because they were embarrassed", 
            "dur": "1.849", 
            "start": "39.815"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because their faces would get very red.", 
            "dur": "2.052", 
            "start": "41.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Well, I tend to get red very quickly.", 
            "dur": "2.235", 
            "start": "43.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s normal, even if I&#39;m not drunk yet.", 
            "dur": "2.093", 
            "start": "45.951"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Is this real, though?", 
            "dur": "1.239", 
            "start": "48.044"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- She was right.", 
            "dur": "1.036", 
            "start": "49.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I still had my doubts too.", 
            "dur": "1.646", 
            "start": "50.319"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I called in some of\nmy fellow Asian co-workers", 
            "dur": "2.011", 
            "start": "51.965"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to help me out.", 
            "dur": "1.118", 
            "start": "53.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, Carol, so do you\nknow what Asian glow is?", 
            "dur": "3.108", 
            "start": "55.094"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I know Asian glow very well.", 
            "dur": "1.971", 
            "start": "58.202"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I turn all red.", 
            "dur": "1.056", 
            "start": "60.173"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not even just my face.", 
            "dur": "1.261", 
            "start": "61.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My whole body just turns red.", 
            "dur": "2.316", 
            "start": "62.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- It just became a part of my life.", 
            "dur": "1.504", 
            "start": "64.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I accepted it.", 
            "dur": "0.976", 
            "start": "66.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- It takes me about\nthree shots to get drunk.", 
            "dur": "2.153", 
            "start": "67.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then maybe like one\nshot to get Asian glow.", 
            "dur": "3.23", 
            "start": "69.439"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Do you feel sick along with the a--", 
            "dur": "1.768", 
            "start": "72.669"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- My heart starts beating\nfaster, or like harder.", 
            "dur": "1.198", 
            "start": "74.437"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And just like really hot\nand uncomfortable and dizzy.", 
            "dur": "4.429", 
            "start": "75.635"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- That sounds delightful.", 
            "dur": "1.057", 
            "start": "80.064"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- It makes me pretty sleepy.", 
            "dur": "1.423", 
            "start": "81.121"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you can&#39;t party when you&#39;re sleepy.", 
            "dur": "2.376", 
            "start": "82.544"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- How would you say it effects\nyou in a social aspect?", 
            "dur": "2.249", 
            "start": "84.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I think as you get older\nyou don&#39;t really care anymore.", 
            "dur": "1.868", 
            "start": "87.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I don&#39;t drink,\nnormally, because of this.", 
            "dur": "2.946", 
            "start": "89.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- People just think you&#39;re an alcoholic.", 
            "dur": "1.666", 
            "start": "91.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Since you do get Asian glow,", 
            "dur": "1.3", 
            "start": "93.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would you mind perhaps\nshowing me that you get--", 
            "dur": "2.682", 
            "start": "94.949"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Sure.", 
            "dur": "0.895", 
            "start": "97.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I got you a Smirnoff Ice.\n- [Carol] Thank you.", 
            "dur": "2.599", 
            "start": "98.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- A popular party drink among the kids.", 
            "dur": "1.992", 
            "start": "101.125"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, as Carol downed her Smirnoff Ice,", 
            "dur": "2.092", 
            "start": "103.117"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Kane and Weston took a shot of tequila.", 
            "dur": "2.052", 
            "start": "105.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Delicious.", 
            "dur": "0.914", 
            "start": "107.261"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then it happened, 15 minutes later", 
            "dur": "2.791", 
            "start": "109.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all three of them bloomed bright red", 
            "dur": "2.128", 
            "start": "111.873"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right before my eyes.", 
            "dur": "1.296", 
            "start": "114.001"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- [Carol] Surprise. My\nstomach gets really red too.", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "116.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Um--", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "119.067"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Don&#39;t you act like\nI&#39;m a monster! (laughs)", 
            "dur": "4.064", 
            "start": "119.817"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I&#39;m just amazed that\nit&#39;s actually happening.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "123.881"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a real thing.", 
            "dur": "0.651", 
            "start": "125.851"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can&#39;t believe it.", 
            "dur": "0.589", 
            "start": "126.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- It&#39;s super real.", 
            "dur": "1.341", 
            "start": "127.091"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it&#39;s like I&#39;m not drunk at all.", 
            "dur": "2.515", 
            "start": "128.432"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Is this something you probably wish", 
            "dur": "1.646", 
            "start": "130.947"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there was like a cure all for?", 
            "dur": "1.706", 
            "start": "132.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Like go to Walgreens and you get a shot", 
            "dur": "1.707", 
            "start": "134.299"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you don&#39;t get Asian\nglow for that whole year.", 
            "dur": "1.869", 
            "start": "136.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- For the whole year?", 
            "dur": "0.631", 
            "start": "137.875"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;d be great!", 
            "dur": "0.71", 
            "start": "138.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Would it actually just turn my stomach", 
            "dur": "2.154", 
            "start": "139.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into that of a white person&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.422", 
            "start": "141.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then I&#39;ll be able to", 
            "dur": "0.935", 
            "start": "142.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "eat all the cheese I want to?", 
            "dur": "1.686", 
            "start": "143.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "0.551", 
            "start": "145.413"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- I don&#39;t think it&#39;ll turn you", 
            "dur": "0.691", 
            "start": "145.964"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into a white person, necessarily.", 
            "dur": "1.117", 
            "start": "146.655"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- [Carol] Phew.", 
            "dur": "0.691", 
            "start": "147.772"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Yeah, wouldn&#39;t it suck to be white?", 
            "dur": "1.646", 
            "start": "148.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- (laughing) Oh fuck that shit.", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "150.109"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And as I looked at my\nnewly red colleagues,", 
            "dur": "2.073", 
            "start": "152.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I accepted it.", 
            "dur": "1.097", 
            "start": "154.132"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a real thing.", 
            "dur": "1.342", 
            "start": "155.229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I thought it&#39;d be\nbest to call in an expert.", 
            "dur": "1.889", 
            "start": "156.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- What causes Asian glow is a build up", 
            "dur": "2.356", 
            "start": "158.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of a toxic metabolite of alcohol.", 
            "dur": "3.23", 
            "start": "160.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Probably about 50% of Asians turn red.", 
            "dur": "3.231", 
            "start": "164.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You drink alcohol,", 
            "dur": "1.28", 
            "start": "167.277"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it gets broken down", 
            "dur": "1.076", 
            "start": "168.557"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into a toxic substance\ncalled acetaldehyde.", 
            "dur": "3.739", 
            "start": "169.633"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s what causes flushing.", 
            "dur": "1.483", 
            "start": "173.372"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It can also cause fast heart rate.", 
            "dur": "2.763", 
            "start": "174.855"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It can cause nausea.", 
            "dur": "1.402", 
            "start": "177.618"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It gives you headaches.", 
            "dur": "0.896", 
            "start": "179.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, that&#39;s bad stuff.", 
            "dur": "1.319", 
            "start": "179.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In Asians, they have a problem", 
            "dur": "2.072", 
            "start": "181.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because they can&#39;t get rid of this.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "183.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, they have an enzyme\nthat actually is maybe", 
            "dur": "3.128", 
            "start": "185.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "50 times more effective at\ngetting rid of the alcohol", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "188.345"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and turning it into this toxic substance.", 
            "dur": "2.397", 
            "start": "191.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And is that what makes us red?", 
            "dur": "1.565", 
            "start": "193.912"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- It makes you red and\ngives you the other things.", 
            "dur": "2.194", 
            "start": "195.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, they don&#39;t really\nget so much of a buzz,", 
            "dur": "2.865", 
            "start": "197.671"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but they have all the toxins", 
            "dur": "1.503", 
            "start": "200.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and so they get all\nthe side effects of it.", 
            "dur": "2.459", 
            "start": "202.039"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Is there anything you\ncould do to mitigate this?", 
            "dur": "2.661", 
            "start": "204.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there a cure?", 
            "dur": "0.833", 
            "start": "207.159"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- My best advice as a\nphysician is don&#39;t drink.", 
            "dur": "4.227", 
            "start": "207.992"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you feel like you have to drink,", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "212.219"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then you can try histamine blockers.", 
            "dur": "3.657", 
            "start": "214.859"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that would be\ncommonly known as Pepcid.", 
            "dur": "3.901", 
            "start": "218.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And there&#39;s nothing\ndangerous about Pepcid?", 
            "dur": "3.191", 
            "start": "222.417"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Yeah, it really inactivates\none of the enzymes", 
            "dur": "3.819", 
            "start": "225.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that breaks down the alcohol.", 
            "dur": "1.665", 
            "start": "229.427"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Basically, the doc is saying", 
            "dur": "2.074", 
            "start": "231.092"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that Pepcid makes you\ndrunker than you should be", 
            "dur": "2.051", 
            "start": "233.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "based on the amount you&#39;ve drank,", 
            "dur": "1.869", 
            "start": "235.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which was good enough\nof a green light for me.", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "237.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I picked up some Pepcid", 
            "dur": "1.383", 
            "start": "239.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and tried it on the only person\nthat would agree to do it.", 
            "dur": "2.702", 
            "start": "241.049"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- This is Pepcid Complete.", 
            "dur": "1.739", 
            "start": "243.751"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(&quot;Ergo&quot;)", 
            "dur": "5", 
            "start": "246.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- And just as strangely\nas the glow appeared,", 
            "dur": "2.397", 
            "start": "252.889"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the glow failed to appear\nwith the use of Pepcid.", 
            "dur": "2.824", 
            "start": "255.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Although it doesn&#39;t work for everybody,", 
            "dur": "1.788", 
            "start": "258.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for Kane, Pepcid definitely worked.", 
            "dur": "2.316", 
            "start": "259.898"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, it does work for some people.", 
            "dur": "1.342", 
            "start": "262.214"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There are solutions out there.", 
            "dur": "1.502", 
            "start": "263.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or is the real take away,", 
            "dur": "1.768", 
            "start": "265.058"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you are gonna still have this,", 
            "dur": "1.077", 
            "start": "266.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you&#39;re not gonna always have that,", 
            "dur": "1.056", 
            "start": "267.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so it may eventually come to the point", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "268.959"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where you just embrace you\nare a part of something", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "271.419"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that a lot of people have.", 
            "dur": "1.321", 
            "start": "273.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- Yeah, and you don&#39;t\nhave to drink, either.", 
            "dur": "1.442", 
            "start": "274.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- So, the next time you go to a bar", 
            "dur": "1.118", 
            "start": "276.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you see a stranger\nwith an unusually red face,", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "277.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just remember, it&#39;s normal.", 
            "dur": "1.504", 
            "start": "279.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you do get Asian glow,", 
            "dur": "1.239", 
            "start": "280.784"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "don&#39;t be embarrassed, be proud.", 
            "dur": "1.503", 
            "start": "282.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s a lot more of you than you think.", 
            "dur": "1.626", 
            "start": "283.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Cheers.", 
            "dur": "0.955", 
            "start": "285.152"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(&quot;Ergo&quot;)", 
            "dur": "5", 
            "start": "286.107"
        }
    ], 
